+| New contributor understands Zend is a private command center | README + architecture doc explain this clearly | Pass |
+| First slice proves mobile gateway without on-device mining | Contributor guide + operator quickstart demonstrate this | Pass |
+| Thin mobile-shaped command-center experience | Documented in contributor guide (index.html) | Pass |
+| Shared PrincipalId contract | Architecture doc + store.py data model documented | Pass |
+| Encrypted operations inbox backed by event spine | **Documented as encrypted but not implemented** | Fail (C1) |
+| Hermes adapter documented | Architecture doc references Hermes adapter boundary | Pass |
+| LAN-only explicitly | Operator quickstart + security notes cover this | Pass |
